parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion steering system can cause loss of steering control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
The failure of the tie rod can cause loss of steering control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
The failure of the power steering pump can cause loss of power steering assist, leading to difficulty steering and potentially causing accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
The failure of the airbag system can lead to unexpected deployment or non-deployment in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: inability to diagnose or repair the issue
cracks in the dashboard near the airbag

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delays or lack of resolution in addressing airbag recalls can leave drivers at risk of injury or death due to faulty airbag systems.
symptoms: inconsistent information from dealerships and manufacturers
and feeling of being at risk due to unresolved recall issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracks in the dashboard near the airbag can compromise the deployment of the airbag in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Cracks in the dashboard near the passenger-side airbag
concern about the safety of repairing the crack due to its proximity to the airbag
and refusal of dealerships and manufacturers to address the issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the vehicle fails to shift gears
the vehicle is stuck in a particular gear
the vehicle stalls or shuts off
the check engine light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PCM can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
the transmission fails to shift gears
the vehicle is stuck in a particular gear
the vehicle stalls or shuts off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the clutch on the torque converter fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission module can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
